#!/usr/bin/env python3
automated_bug_hunter_full.py
Comprehensive, robust recon script (Subdomains -> Ports -> Tech -> Screenshots -> Reports)

Usage:
    python3 automated_bug_hunter_full.py example.com
    python3 automated_bug_hunter_full.py --target example.com --no-screenshot --no-nmap

Requirements:
    pip3 install requests beautifulsoup4 python-docx
    # optional:
    pip3 install python-nmap selenium sublist3r
    # For selenium screenshots: install Chrome/Chromium and chromedriver matching your browser.